REF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bfantasystoriesforum.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ryvian>Ryvian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Warlord of Delnor</span><br>  Posts: 205<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/19/02 8:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Ok here goes, older bro to the resuce</span><hr size=1> Walking down the street, Andrew looked around the crowd. He walked into the closest shop he could find. &quot;Umm exuse me, but could you help me? I'm trying to find a girl, I don't have a picture. Only a name, Nefertiti. Have you seen her or heard of her name?&quot; Andy looked at the shop keeper's blank stare. Taking it as his answer Andy turned and walked out of the store. About to give up, this was like looking for a needle in a stack of needles. Sighing and walking out into the crowded street Andy looked back up to the buildings upon buildings of the city. This was going to take forever.<br>
