s them. When she was a kid she used to go to the orphanage all the time to play with Derek and the other kids. (says so in the other rp :P). i'm rambling on n such. lol. ANYWAYS. nefertiti's color i forget but she was likeableness or loveableness or something like that. so i just summed up my char... o.O lol, back to the rp!)<br>
