d have called for an ambulance, or used his mentalities to try and heal his friend, but he knew engaging his own mind could only do more harm than good and an ambulance would draw to much attention on them.  The things he had stolen last he had left were of no small value.  Not knowing exactly what to do, he told Carmen he'd go get some clean cloths and warm water to clean his wounds.  God, why, why did the world have to keep closing in on him, why.<br>
